OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FAs cross-party groups of new MSPs
OL,7,Fshuttle around parliament's sunlit
OL,8,Fcorridors like schools of fish,
OL,9,Fthere's an element of wide-eyed glee
OL,10,Famongst the first-timers.
OL,12,FLet's see how long that lasts.
OL,14,FThis has been a smooth introduction
OL,15,Ffor the Scottish parliament newbies,
OL,16,Fwith guided tours taking place
OL,17,Falongside sessions showing them how to
OL,18,Faccess their offices, IT and claim
OL,19,Fexpenses.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
