CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FPretty standard first day at work
OL,7,Fstuff, apart from the fact that you
OL,8,Fcount most of the other people around
OL,9,Fyou as opponents.
OL,11,FThat's why the introductory groups are
OL,12,Fcross-party.
OL,14,FIt's aimed at breaking down barriers
OL,15,Fthat will inevitably build up as the
OL,16,Fsession progresses and encouraging
OL,17,FMSPs to see the human in each other
OL,18,Frather than the politician.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
