CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FOne new Reform member was pleased to
OL,7,Freport they have not yet been refused
OL,8,Fa handshake despite the vitriol
OL,9,Fbetween their party and opponents in
OL,10,Fthe run up to last week's Holyrood
OL,11,Felection.
OL,13,FBut politics starts for real on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FThat's when a new presiding officer,
OL,17,Fthe equivalent of the speaker in the
OL,18,FHouse of Commons, will be selected by
OL,19,FMSPs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
