CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FWhipping operations are already at
OL,7,Fplay with the SNP said to be pushing
OL,8,Fbackbencher Claire Haughey as their
OL,9,Fchoice.
OL,11,FThis has been widely derided by
OL,12,Fopposition parties and indeed by some
OL,13,Fnationalists who believe she would be
OL,14,Fa "patsy" for the government.
OL,16,FThat may not be helped by the fact of
OL,17,Fa cabinet minister leading the push
OL,18,Ffor Ms Haughey, who last session
OL,19,Fchaired the health committee, to
OL,20,Fbecome the parliament's impartial
OL,21,Fwatchdog.
OL,26,@vD@COUvD@IO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
