PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FA move is on to persuade Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat Liam McArthur, who brought
OL,8,Fthe assisted dying bill to parliament,
OL,9,Fto stand and it is thought that he
OL,10,Fwould have the backing of multiple
OL,11,Fopposition members, including the
OL,12,FScottish Greens.
OL,14,FIf he secured the support of all
OL,15,Fopposition members, he would win
OL,16,Fbecause the SNP does not have a
OL,17,Fmajority.
OL,19,FThat lack of total control will not
OL,20,Fstop John Swinney being re-elected
OL,21,Ffirst minister next week, though.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
