CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FA formal process has to be followed in
OL,7,Fline with Holyrood's rules, with the
OL,8,Fvote scheduled for next Tuesday, but
OL,9,Fhe will be back in post and then we
OL,10,Fcan expect a new cabinet in the
OL,11,Ffollowing days.
OL,13,FHe has some big decisions to make with
OL,14,Ffour of his top ministerial team `
OL,15,FKate Forbes, Shona Robison, Mairi
OL,16,FGougeon and Fiona Hyslop ` standing
OL,17,Fdown and a fifth, Angus Robertson,
OL,18,Flosing his seat.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
