OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778760670
OL,3,CGrown up politics is about to kick in
OL,4,Cfor Holyrood's new kids on the block
OL,6,FHow Mr Swinney reshuffles, and what he
OL,7,Fdoes with ambitious newcomers like
OL,8,Fformer SNP Westminster leader Stephen
OL,9,FFlynn, will tell us a lot about how he
OL,10,Fplans to run his new government.
OL,12,FAt that point it's sink or swim time
OL,13,Ffor the new ministers ` and those
OL,14,Ftasked with holding them to account.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
